ms can be returned for a full refund. Final Sale Items To help keep our customers and associates safe Walmart and Marketplace sellers will not replace, accept returns, or provide refunds for: Alcohol (Beer, Wine, Spirits) Airsoft &amp; Air Guns Ammunition (including powder, pellets, primer) Archery Bows BB Guns Bear Spray Collectibles (i.e., Labubu items) Crossbows Diabetic Supplies* (including meters, strips lancet devices &amp; syringes) Gas Powered Recreational Vehicles (e.g., Dirt Bikes, Mini-Bikes, Go-Carts, Scooters, Ride-ons, UTVs &amp; ATVs) Home Diagnostic Testing Kits (including COVID-19 tests) Hygienic Medical Equipment (e.g., bedpans, bath seats, eye drop guides, opened/unsealed breast pumps, sitz baths) Items containing pseudoephedrine, ephedrine, phenylpropanolamine Firearms Ovulation &amp; Pregnancy Tests Precious Metals (e.g., gold bars, coins, currency) Prescription Medications and Devices Pepper Spray RV sewer lines, toilets, toilet bowls and urinals (used or installed) Sex Toys &amp; Vibrators Special orders made through Walmart Business Tires, Wheels, Rims, Snow Tires (used or mounted) Tobacco Products Trading cards (opened or unopened) Vertical Bows *Diabetic supplies and items covered by Medicare Part B that are deemed substandard or unsuitable per Medicare supplier standards are returnable. Other Final Sale Service Items &amp; Digital Products: Gift Cards Prepaid Cell Phone Cards Prepaid Gaming Cards Sim Cards Video Game Download Cards Video On Demand Unless specified, electronic games and software downloads are not returnable after purchase. If you did not receive an email containing the code or are unable to redeem the code provided, please go to walmart.com/help , scroll to the bottom of the page and click the blue Contact Us button. Financial/Home/Tech Services: Return/Refund/Replacement Policy Final Sale Items: Eligible Items with a Receipt*: Eligible via Service Providers Only: Walmart Express Bill Payments Money Transfer Home Services (